<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, height=device-height, initial-scale=1">
		
		<title>홈 화면</title>
		
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"> <!-- load bootstrap css -->
    	<link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.min.css"> <!-- load fontawesome -->
    	
    	<style>
        	body { padding-top:80px; }

			.home{
				color : indianred;
			}

			@font-face {
				font-family: 'Nanum Gothic'; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;
				src: url('../public/font/BMDOHYEON_ttf.ttf');
				src: local('NanumGothic'),
					url('../public/font/BMDOHYEON_ttf.ttf') format('embedded-opentype'),
					url('../public/font/BMDOHYEON_ttf.ttf') format('woff2'),
					url('../public/font/BMDOHYEON_ttf.ttf') format('woff'),
					url('../public/font/BMDOHYEON_ttf.ttf') format('truetype');
			}
        	
        	h1, p, a { font-family: 'Nanum Gothic' ; color : ghostwhite;}


    	</style>
    
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
		    <div class="jumbotron text-center" style='background-image:url("/public/images/sample2.jpg")' >
		        <h1><div class="home"  style="color: firebrick" id="police" ></div> 경찰관 로그인 화면</h1>
				<br>
				<% if (login_success) { %>
					<p>로그인되어 있습니다.</p>
					<br>
					<a href="/logout" class="btn btn-default"><span class="fa fa-user"></span>로그아웃</a>
				<% } else { %>
					<p>로그인하세요.<p>
					<p>계정이 없으시면 회원가입하세요.</p>
					<br>
			        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-default"><span class="fa fa-user"></span>로그인</a>
			        <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-default"><span class="fa fa-user"></span>회원가입</a>
					<br>

				<% } %>
				
		    </div>
		
		</div>
	</body>
</html>